        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-ico">Col</div>
          <h4>Collagen Peptides</h4>
          <p>Provides amino acids (proline, glycine) for hair structure and follicle support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
