      <p>Viviscal stands apart from most competitors because it has genuine clinical data behind its proprietary AminoMar marine complex. Published studies in peer-reviewed journals have demonstrated statistically significant improvements in hair density and diameter among participants using the Viviscal system over a six-month period. The gummy format makes this clinical-grade approach more accessible to people who dislike swallowing pills. The marine collagen provides amino acids (proline and glycine) that directly support keratin formation, while zinc contributes to protein synthesis and cell division in hair follicles. If evidence-based supplementation matters to you and you are not restricted by a vegan diet, Viviscal is one of the strongest choices on the market.</p>

